caption: I wish more people would have looked up while they were walking through that street. What a cool sight... this is a true ecosystem, full of birds and flowers. Absolutely fantastic to look at.
Cool little site. Nice spot to sit and eat lunch
You almost can't find the house anymore... Great idea... It would also be great to see from the inside
Very quiet area. You can sit and contemplate the pretty view of the vertical garden
This little vertical jungle is very cool.
